  ANIMALS OF THE WORLD
============================================================

Name:         Snow Leopard
Scientific:   Panthera uncia
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Mountain
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       55 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Cannot roar; uses long tail as blanket; leaps 15 meters

Name:         Giant Panda
Scientific:   Ailuropoda melanoleuca
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Temperate forest
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     20 years
Weight:       100 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Eats 12-38 kg bamboo daily; has a sixth finger (pseudo-thumb)

Name:         Axolotl
Scientific:   Ambystoma mexicanum
Class:        Amphibia
Habitat:      Lakes
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       0.3 kg
Status:       Critically Endangered
Fact:         Can regenerate entire limbs, spine, heart, and brain tissue

